invalidateTest
├── given escape hatch is not configured
│   └── it should proceed with normal invalidation logic
└── given escape hatch is configured
    ├── when escape hatch is not open for the checkpoint epoch
    │   └── it should proceed with normal invalidation logic
    └── when escape hatch is open for the checkpoint epoch
        └── it should revert with Rollup__CannotInvalidateEscapeHatch
